heading: Oldstones Dungeon Guide
content: Oldstones has one of the biggest damage aspects for every class, . On top of that, it's a fairly decent dungeon for grinding, so if you have a Nightmare Sigil you may consider running it here. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
